Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all cases

Name: Number of times SW-Checklist Completed occurs in the entire event log
Percentage of cases where SW-Checklist Completed is immediately followed by SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Frequency of SW-Checklist Completed appearing after Plagiarism Originality Report Completed across all variants
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Ratio of SW-Checklist Completed to SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion across all process instances
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'

Name: Percentage of variants in which SW-Checklist Completed appears exactly once
Metric: the average of the function base == 1 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Number of SW-Checklist Completed events that occur within 24 hours of Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: Number of 'SW-Checklist Completed' activities for cases where activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' occurs

Name: Frequency of SW-Checklist Completed in cases that ultimately result in SW-EIC Reject compared to cases resulting in SW-EIC Accept
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed events that are part of the most frequent variant pattern
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all cases

Name: Number of cases where SW-Checklist Completed is delayed beyond a checklist due reminder (e.g., occurs after SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days)
Metric: Number of 'SW-Checklist Completed' activities for cases where activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed executions performed by the SYSTEM performer relative to all SYSTEM-performed activities
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all cases

Name: Ratio of SW-Checklist Completed to Manuscript Export Succeeded across the entire log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed occurrences that are not preceded by any reminder activity (e.g., SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days or SW-Checklist Completion now due)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all cases

Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed activities that lead directly to reviewer assignment phases (e.g., SW-Initial Reviewer Selection or SW-AE Assign Reviewers) within the same case
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all cases

Name: Percentage of cases in which SW-Checklist Completed is followed by any form of revision decision (SW-EIC Major Revision, SW-EIC Minor Revision, or SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all cases
